Since we deal with non-canonicalized surface forms of instances, we maintained a list of aliases, obtained from Wikidata, for the annotated prominent instances. 
An instance is relevant if its length-normalized Levenshtein distance [navarro2001guided] from any of the aliases is less than 0.1.